your saltshaker for a bottle of soy sauce may help reduce your risk of blood clots p A recent study revealed that soy sauce contains antiplatelet compounds that may help thin the blood This in turn could help reduce the risk of clotting and stroke Just remember however that soy sauce is high in sodium If you choose soy sauce to season your food use it sparingly just as you would table salt br br
